statements: SELECT id, domain_name, creation_date, last_accessed, is_malicious FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT domain_name, creation_date, is_malicious, last_accessed, id FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT id, creation_date, last_accessed, domain_name, is_malicious FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT domain_name, is_malicious FROM phishing_domains WHERE creation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, domain_name, is_malicious FROM phishing_domains WHERE last_accessed < '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains WHERE domain_name = 'example.com';
SELECT domain_name, creation_date FROM phishing_domains ORDER BY creation_date DESC;
SELECT id, domain_name FROM phishing_domains WHERE is_malicious = TRUE ORDER BY last_accessed ASC;
SELECT id, domain_name, last_accessed FROM phishing_domains WHERE creation_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains WHERE is_malicious = TRUE AND creation_date >= '2022-01-01' AND last_accessed < '2022-07-01';
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT id, domain_name, ip_address FROM phishing_domains WHERE country = 'USA';
SELECT domain_name, ip_address, country FROM phishing_domains ORDER BY domain_name DESC;
SELECT domain_name, ip_address, date_discovered FROM phishing_domains WHERE date_discovered BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT report_id, domain_id, report_description FROM phishing_reports WHERE report_status = 'Pending';
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains WHERE country='USA' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT domain_name, ip_address, country FROM phishing_domains WHERE country IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM phishing_reports WHERE report_status='Pending' ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT domain_name, ip_address, DATE_FORMAT(date_discovered, '%Y-%m-%d') AS discovered_date FROM phishing_domains ORDER BY discovered_date;
SELECT phishing_reports.report_id, phishing_reports.report_description, phishing_domains.domain_name FROM phishing_reports JOIN phishing_domains ON phishing_reports.domain_id = phishing_domains.id;
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT domain_name, registration_date FROM phishing_domains WHERE is_active = TRUE;
SELECT domain_name, detection_date FROM phishing_domains WHERE registration_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT domain_name, report_date, reporter_name FROM phishing_reports ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT domain_name, check_result, check_description FROM phishing_checks WHERE check_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains WHERE is_active = TRUE;
SELECT domain_name, registration_date, detection_date FROM phishing_domains ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT domain_name, reporter_name, report_reason FROM phishing_domains JOIN phishing_reports ON phishing_domains.domain_id = phishing_reports.domain_id;
SELECT domain_name, check_date, check_result, check_description FROM phishing_domains JOIN phishing_checks ON phishing_domains.domain_id = phishing_checks.domain_id ORDER BY check_date ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_domains, AVG(DATEDIFF(detection_date, registration_date)) AS avg_detection_time FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT domain_name, registrar FROM phishing_domains WHERE status = 'active';
SELECT attempt_id, source_ip, timestamp FROM phishing_attempts ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT domain_id, domain_name, created_date FROM phishing_domains WHERE created_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT report_id, reporter_email, severity FROM phishing_reports WHERE severity >= 3;
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT domain_name, registrar, status FROM phishing_domains ORDER BY domain_name ASC;
SELECT domain_id, domain_name, created_date FROM phishing_domains WHERE status='active';
SELECT * FROM phishing_attempts WHERE success=true AND timestamp>'2021-01-01';
SELECT domain_id, reporter_email, severity FROM phishing_reports WHERE severity>1 ORDER BY severity DESC;
SELECT * FROM phishing_domains;
SELECT domain_name, registrar, status FROM phishing_domains ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT id, email_address, sender_ip FROM phishing_emails WHERE status = 'blocked';
SELECT * FROM phishing_reports WHERE status = 'pending' ORDER BY report_date ASC;
SELECT victim_name, email_address, phone_number FROM phishing_victims WHERE status = 'resolved';

SELECT domain_name, registrar FROM phishing_domains WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
